abstract:
For each of the following conditions, we characterize the pseudovarieties of
semigroups V that satisfy it: (i) every epimorphism to a member of V is onto;
(ii) every epimorphism to a finite semigroup with domain a member of V is onto;
(iii) for every epimorphism from S to T with S in V and T finite, T is also a
member of V.
